    "Abstracting with credit is permitted.",
    "To copy otherwise, or republish, to post on servers or to redistribute to lists, requires prior specific permission and/or a fee.",
    "Request permissions from permissions@acm.org.",
    "Out-of-date and long-tail knowledge lead to LLMs struggling with hallucinations and factual errors, especially in knowledge-intensive tasks.To address these issues, an emerging approach is Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG) [4,15,21,51].",
    "Instead of relying solely on LLM's inherent knowledge, RAG augments LLMs with external knowledge retrieved from large corpora or knowledge databases."
  ]
}